== Umugambi ==
Mu 1886, Percy Fitzpatrick w'imyaka 20 ukomoka mu mujyi wa Cape Town yerekeje ku kirwa cya Delagoa muri Transvaal gucukura zahabu<ref>Jock of the Bushveld's happy ending – in 3D - Gauteng Film ... <nowiki>http://www.gautengfilm.org.za</nowiki> › ... › November 2010</ref>. Agezeyo, abuza icyana cy'imbwa, Jock, kurohama arakirera<ref>Jock of the Bushveld to make history in SA's first 3D feature film <nowiki>https://www.filmcontact.com</nowiki> › south-africa › jock-bush...</ref>. Iyo amaherezo Percy ageze iyo yerekeza, nta zahabu iba ikiriho, nuko atangira kuba umuyobozi. Nyuma yaho, we na Jock babayeho mubyabaye byinshi birimo inyamaswa zo mwishyamba hamwe nabashoferi batwaraga abacakara<ref>Johnny Clegg writes music for Jock of the Bushveld (filmcontact.com)</ref>.  

